data.value:
version 1.5 changelog 1. Optimized the RAM usage of the app, there was memory leak in the app now it is Solved. 2. Added the Games Optimization tab. 3. Added more new Buttons. 4. Major UI changes and improvement of Screenshot Way Instructions. 5. Added the ISLC Software to bin folder of this app. 6. Added the feature of disabling HPET. 7. Some minor UI improvements.
version 1.4.1 changelog 1. Minor UI changes. 2. Added new features to UI, but removed them because they were causing problems. 3. Increased the size of the tabs to click them easily, before it was difficult to change the tab by clicking them.
version 1.4 changelog 1. Added the Tabbed Feature. 2. Added 7 NEW tabs. 3. Docked majority of the controls, this makes software resizeable according to screens (AKA Responsive Software). 4. Added the Donation and Subscribe Buttons. 5. No new buttons were added but What's New Button was removed from Other Options. 6. Major UI Improvement.
version 1.3 changelog 1. Added the What's New Form instead of using Notepad. 2. Added the Confirmation message on Logoff Buton. 3. Changed the color of the main form. 4. Added the new class for Dynamic Resize. 5. Some Minor Changes on UI. 6. Added The Comming Soon Lable on the other options section instead of just keeping the blank box.
version 1.2 changelog 1. whole software was made from scratch again on vb6 framework. 2. some minor UI changes. 3. removed the Private Browser Button (due to less or no use of it at all). 4. fixed SSD Trim Only C Drive Button (earlier it was showing command not found). 5. added new label with 2022. 6. used new fonts that looks good. 7. removed the splash screen to load the app faster. 8. added log off button to quickly reboot system. 9. added Disk Clean-up button to clean drives junk.
version 1.1 changelog 1. introduced %USERNAME% to fetch the current user name automatically. 2. added power options to perform power related task like shutdown restart sleep etc. 3. added Private Browser to access any website for temporary without making any history or cookies traces and no java script enabled. 4. added whats new button to show this Help message and added a new button What's new and it redirects to my youube video. 5. added link to my channel when clicked on my picture Sahil Bhandari. 6. added icon and splash screen to make it look more beautiful. 7. some minor UI Changes.
initial release: Thank you for using my Software. no need to pay any thing its free for all. its currently in initial release stage, if you need any extra features please tell me. to make every thing work just follow these steps. 1. just edit the file called cleanscript and change username from 'sahil' to your's computer user name. 2. do not delete any .dlls or .bat files it will break the software. 3. use it wisely and regularly OK!
